name: CDISC Controlled Terminology Standard Type
preferredTerm: CDISC Define-XML CDISC Controlled Terminology Standard Type Terminology

terms.definition: The terminology subset that includes terms pertaining to the Clinical Data Interchange Standards Consortium (CDISC) Analysis Data Model (ADaM).
The terminology subset that includes terms relevant to the Clinical Data Interchange Standards Consortium (CDISC) Clinical Data Acquisition Standards Harmonization (CDASH) group.
The terminology subset that includes terms relevant to the Clinical Data Interchange Standards Consortium (CDISC) Define-XML standard.
The terminology subset that includes terms pertaining to the Clinical Data Interchange Standards Consortium (CDISC) Study Data Tabulation Model (SDTM).
The terminology subset that includes terms relevant to the Clinical Data Interchange Standards Consortium (CDISC) Standard for Exchange of Non-clinical Data (SEND) group.
